Manga Studio EX 5.0.5 Windows

How To Install 

Plz Dear Friendz Read Carefuly Do Each Step CareFully 
For Better Understand Please Check The Folder *Help For Activation Pictures*

Recommended

"Your Antivirus May Warn You About Keygen. Ignore It If Happens, 
It Is Just A False Positive"

01: *IMPORTANT* Close internet connection Before You Run The Program. 

2. Install application, double click "Install Manga Studio.exe" 
(with admin rights on your system.)

3. Open the application.

4. Run keygen "xf-sms505ex.exe" in "Keygen X-Force" folder. 

a. Click on Generate, copy and paste it in to application. Click on
"Register license" (You may need to enter the serial manually.)

* All characters uppercase and all O are ZERO. 

b. Select "Verify license right now" ==> Next 

c. Select "Perform manually
" ==> Next

d. - Delete the words in "request" area in keygen and
- Copy the license Authentication Key into the keygen and click on
the "Activate" button. (IMPORTANT : Copy each block without spaces)

e. Copy this code to application and click "Next"

5. Do not update the application
